# Splunk DNS Log Analysis Lab Instructions

## Objective
- Ingest Zeek-style DNS logs into Splunk
- Extract information such as DNS query types, source hosts, and most queried domains
- Build SPL queries to investigate DNS activity
- Detect anomalies such as failed resolutions and high-latency lookups

